--------------------------------------
GHC 7.8.4 Linux cross-compiler for ARM
--------------------------------------

Congratulations! You are the proud owner of a GHC ARM cross
compilation environment.

Installed compilers
-------------------

There are two versions of the compiler installed.

1. One that targets the host architecture (x86_64)

   ~/.ghc/arm-host/bin/ghc

2. One that targets the ARM achitecture

  /root/x-tools/arm-plum-linux-gnueabi/bin/arm-plum-linux-gnueabi-ghc


Environment variables
---------------------

The PATH has been extended with the path to the cross-compiler.
To access the host compiler use the prefix $GHC_HOST/bin. e.g.

  $ $GHC_HOST/bin/ghc --version

